 hai B\'aan k\'fd k\'d5t l\'b5m cho hay s\'cf l\'b5m cho \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'e3 ph\'b6i n\'e9p thu\'d5 kh\'abng \'ae\'f3ng theo nh\'f7ng quy \'ae\'denh c\'f1a Hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh n\'b5y, l\'f3c \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'e8i t\'ad\'eeng n\'b5y c\'e3 th\'d3 gi
